STATE
v.
Karenna T. JONES. No. 238P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 8, 2006. Adrian M. Lapas, Goldsboro, for Karenna T. Jones. William Graham, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th day of May 2006 by Attorney General for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 8th day of May 2006."
